msgstr "Henkilökohtaisen tilin PDF neljännesvuosittain."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:1960
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:3101
