msgstr "**Lyhennetty malli**"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:2422
msgid ""
"PDF: `Abridged Social Balance Sheet PDF <https://www.nbb.be/doc/ba/models/"
