#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:5
msgid "Hong Kong"
msgstr "Hongkong"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:7
msgid ""
"The Hong Kong payroll localization ensures all salary computations strictly "
"comply with the `Employment Ordinance (Cap. 57) <https://www.labour.gov.hk/"
"eng/legislat/content2.htm>`_ and `Inland Revenue Department (IRD) <https://"
"www.ird.gov.hk/eng/ese/erc.htm>`_ requirements. This includes automated "
"calculations for Mandatory Provident Fund (MPF) contributions, the "
"generation of IR56 reports, and the processing of leave payments such as "
"Payment in Lieu of Notice, Severance Payments (SP), and Long Service "
"Payments (LSP)—fully updated for the 2025 MPF offsetting transition rules."
msgstr ""
"Hongkongin palkkahallinnon lokalisointi varmistaa, että kaikki "
"palkkalaskelmat noudattavat tarkasti `Employment Ordinance (Cap. 57) "
"<https://www.labour.gov.hk/eng/legislat/content2.htm>`_ ja `Inland Revenue "
"Department (IRD) <https://www.ird.gov.hk/eng/ese/erc.htm>`_ vaatimuksia. "
"Tämä sisältää automaattisen laskemisen Mandatory Provident Fund (MPF) "
"-maksuille, IR56-raporttien luomisen ja lomapalkkioiden käsittelyn, kuten "
"Payment in Lieu of Notice, Severance Payments (SP) ja Long Service Payments "
"(LSP) – täysin päivitettynä vuoden 2025 MPF-kuittaussiirtymäsäännöille."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/hong_kong.rst:16
msgid ""
"Before configuring the Hong Kong localization, refer to the "
"general :doc:`payroll <../../payroll>` documentation. It covers foundational "
"information applicable to all localizations, including universal settings, "
"salary structures, and global payroll fields."
msgstr ""
"Ennen Hongkongin lokalisoinnin määrittämistä tutustu "
"yleiseen :doc:`palkkahallinto <../../payroll>`dokumentaatioon. Se kattaa "
"perustavanlaatuiset tiedot, jotka koskevat kaikkia lokalisointeja, mukaan "
"lukien yleiset asetukset, palkkarakenteet ja yleiset palkkahallintokentät."

